The Managing Director/CEO of Explicit Communications, Tunde Thani, has expressed delight over the success of Veleta Sparkling Fruit Drink advert currently making waves on television across the country. The jingle-led TV commercial dubbed ‘Veleta Moments’, created by Thani’s company, which debuted in April 2022, has received positive reviews and attracted a large following of enthusiastic audience, making it one of the most talked about commercials at the moment. The TV Commercial engages the audience through relatable life scenarios that cut across, celebrating the beauty in modern family, friendship and togetherness.   Interglobe IEG, others invest in pharmaceutical production…     DFIs can boost agribusiness, infrastructure growth-BoI boss     2023 elections: Experts fear economy may collapse   Speaking recently on the success of the commercial, Thani said, “I couldn’t be more elated on the successful execution of such an amazing project; this has been one of my proudest moments. We currently have people talking about this commercial daily. I am particularly happy that we have been able to keep the dream of celebration alive with Veleta Sparkling Fruit Drink.” Speaking on behalf of Veleta Sparkling Fruit Drink, the Head of Marketing, Mr Bolaji Alalade of Intercontinental Distillers Limited, said, “We are quite happy with the direction of the TVC, as it clearly interprets the celebration moments that is the brand’s promise.’’